{"type": "article", "id": 30699, "title": "磁性控制的自动铅笔", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-07T22:52:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016080720494254UIadsMDTJXlovC.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>由设计团队 <a href=\"http://hribarcain.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">HRIBARCAIN</a> 推出的 MAGNO 是一支富有未来感的自动铅笔，利用磁性来精准地调整铅芯，免去了过去需要一点点通过按钮来调整的麻烦。MAGNO 的铅芯由一块钕磁固定，转动笔套尾部的开关将笔芯解锁后，笔芯就会根据金属圆环的位置移动。MAGNO 的笔套由航空级别的铝材料制成，极简的设计看起来干净利落，不仔细看或许还会错认为钢笔。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/238708282/magno-the-worlds-first-magnetically-controlled-pen\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 25 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807213311pfSVHrqlGycIXPJw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.857353\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807213311w4FIVj6UYG7r5Xzv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.857353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160807213311tKJzuoZA4SRBIW0l.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.794118\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}